jor final, the Canadian was delighted with her showing on the biggest stage and was clearly enjoying her moment in the limelight.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999988667811576, \"rank\": 1.1332187846106756e-06, \"text\": \"Newman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\"}, {\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9615875326184611, \"rank\": 0.039935345834643164, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"a major final\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"her moment\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"the limelight\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After successfully making it over the 4.85m mark with her second attempt, Newman initially appeared to have picked up an injury before breaking into a magnificent twerking celebration - prompting loud cheers from the nearby fans.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999988667811576, \"rank\": 1.1332187846106756e-06, \"text\": \"Newman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 4.85m mark\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"her second attempt\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"a magnificent twerking celebration\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"loud cheers\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearby fans\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The celebration has since gone viral across social media, with Newman - who also models on OnlyFans - later joking that she may have to get a photograph of the moment framed.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999988667811576, \"rank\": 1.1332187846106756e-06, \"text\": \"Newman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The celebration\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"OnlyFans\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"a photograph\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tam 112 y\\u00c4\\u00b1l sonra bir Kanadal\\u00c4\\u00b1 s\\u00c4\\u00b1r\\u00c4\\u00b1kla atlamada madalya kazand\\u00c4\\u00b1 ve 4.85'le Kanada rekoru k\\u00c4\\u00b1rd\\u00c4\\u00b1\\u00c4\\u009f\\u00c4\\u00b1 atlay\\u00c4\\u00b1\\u00c5\\u009ftan sonra twerk yapt\\u00c4\\u00b1!Kar\\u00c5\\u009f\\u00c4\\u00b1n\\u00c4\\u00b1zda, the one and only Alysha Newman!pic.twitter.com/nwwwtPZdMG Speaking at a press conference immediately after the action, an ecstatic Newman said she 'loved every moment' of the final in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kosovo_Liberation_Army\", \"score\": 0.9999999883752936, \"rank\": 1.1624513874601261e-08, \"text\": \"kla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kosovo_Liberation_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kosovo_Liberation_Army\"}, {\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanada_(family_of_ragas)\", \"score\": 0.6275509260069373, \"rank\": 0.5735294117648758, \"text\": \"Kanada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanada_(family_of_ragas)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanada_(family_of_ragas)\"}, {\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999988667811576, \"rank\": 1.1332187846106756e-06, \"text\": \"Newman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8813203961737145, \"rank\": 0.11389859746174923, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kazand\\u00c4\\u00b1\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"twerk yapt\\u00c4\\u00b1!Kar\\u00c5\\u009f\\u00c4\\u00b1n\\u00c4\\u00b1zda\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"every moment\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the bronze-medallist admitted she was close to 'sharing some words' with stewards inside the stadium after her coach almost got himself booted out of his seat in the stands.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze-medallist\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"some words\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"stewards\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"his seat\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's been five years since I have been in a final, so for me to wrap around and jump pretty intense, back-to-back with 48 hours in between, was a challenge for me to not get to excited, but not be too relaxed,' Newman told reporters.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999988667811576, \"rank\": 1.1332187846106756e-06, \"text\": \"Newman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"48 hours\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I would say that the one thing that really kind of got me angry\\u2026 not mad or angry\\u2026 but fuelled me actually more was looking over in the stands and seeing my coach almost getting kicked out of his seat.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the one thing\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"his seat\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So I definitely had to take a couple of breaths for that because my coach is my best friend.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"breaths\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"my best friend\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would do anything for me and I would do the same.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was very close to sharing some words over there and really letting them know that of course we understand that there is more than 12 girls in the final, but it's important and it's an event that needs coaches present.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some words\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 12 girls\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Maybe future-wise, we look at getting coaches between the stands and where the photographers are and maybe a little coaching section.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"the photographers\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And you guys could sell more tickets and make more money and then we could have those coaches down on the in-field that we can actually communicate with and not feel like we are stopping people's view as well.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"more tickets\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"more money\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"those coaches\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"the in-field\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"people's view\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was hard for me.'\", \"from\": 3059,